&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Assistant Branch Manager:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Assistant Branch Manager supports the Branch Manager in the&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;overall performance of the branch&lt;/strong&gt;, including sales, collections, and team development.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role helps drive daily execution, supports coworkers in meeting expectations, and assists with maintaining a structured, results-focused branch environment. The Assistant Branch Manager may provide direction to coworkers, help coach the team, serve as a leadership support role, and may help run the branch in the absence of the Branch Manager.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What This Role Requires&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires someone who is comfortable:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting branch performance goals and helping drive results&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assisting with team leadership and daily follow-up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Holding coworkers to clear expectations with guidance from the Branch Manager&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Having direct conversations with customers about payments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating in a structured, metric-driven environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing multiple priorities in a fast-paced setting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Setting a professional example for coworkers through urgency, organization, and accountability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Performance Expectations&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful Assistant Branch Managers:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the Branch Manager in achieving branch goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow up consistently on assigned tasks and customer accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help coach and develop coworkers to improve performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Address issues quickly and involve the Branch Manager when needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain structure and organization in daily operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with sales, collections, lending, and customer service execution&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help ensure company policies and procedures are followed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate readiness to take on increased leadership responsibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Compensation &amp;amp; Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive hourly compensation + bonus potential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Majority company paid Health, Dental and Vision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401k Program&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company Paid - Life and Disability Insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 Weeks paid Vacation, 6 paid Holidays, 2 PTO and 5 Sick days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;40hr Work Week – Monday thru Saturday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Branch hours: Mon - Fri 10am – 6pm, Sat 9am – 1pm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Every Sunday Off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;$18/hr.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monthly bonus potential&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;Minimum Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School Diploma or equivalent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work scheduled hours, including Saturdays&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Valid Driver’s License and reliable transportation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successful completion of pre-employment screening&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Manager in Training:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Looking for a role where you can grow fast and develop real-world skills? In this position, you’ll work directly with customers—asking the right questions, overcoming objections, and guiding them through decisions, including financial conversations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you thrive in a fast-paced environment, are open to feedback and coaching, and can stay motivated even when you hear “no,” this role offers a strong opportunity to build confidence, resilience, and a solid foundation in sales.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Scope&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a &lt;strong&gt;customer-facing, performance-driven role&lt;/strong&gt; where you will work directly with customers to understand their needs and guide them through financial solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will handle both inbound and outbound conversations, ask follow-up questions, and help customers make decisions—including conversations about money.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role requires someone who is comfortable:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;asking direct questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;handling hesitation or rejection&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;making outbound calls&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;staying engaged in conversations that may feel uncomfortable at times&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Success Looks Like&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Successful team members:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay positive and engaged, even when customers hesitate or say no&lt;br&gt;• Ask follow-up questions instead of ending conversations&lt;br&gt;• Build confidence quickly through practice and coaching&lt;br&gt;• Take feedback and apply it immediately&lt;br&gt;• Perform consistently in a structured, goal-driven environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Work With Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Start your career with an industry leader where you will receive structured training and ongoing coaching.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fast-track advancement opportunities&lt;br&gt;• Team environment focused on your success&lt;br&gt;• Competitive compensation with bonus potential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Majority company paid Health, Dental and Vision&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401k Program&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Company Paid - Life and Disability Insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2 Weeks paid Vacation, 6 paid Holidays, 2 PTO and 5 Sick days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;40hr Work Week – Monday thru Saturday&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Branch hours: Mon - Fri 10am – 6pm, Sat 9am – 1pm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Every Sunday Off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;$13.35 - $15.24/hr.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Monthly bonus potential&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Preferred Experience&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Customer service, sales, or collections experience&lt;br&gt;• Comfortable speaking with customers over the phone and in person&lt;br&gt;• Strong communication skills&lt;br&gt;• Ability to learn quickly and adapt&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum Requirements&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High School Diploma or equivalent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be able to work 40 hours per week, including Saturdays.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Satisfactory completion of pre-employment screenings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reliable form of personal transportation and valid Driver’s License&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in English and Spanish a plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The above statements are intended to describe the general nature and level of work being performed. They are not intended to be an exhaustive list of responsibilities, duties and skills required.&lt;/p&gt;
